ComicInfo.Title: Chapter 5 & The Artwork!
ComicInfo.Summary: SuperMilo, trying to sleep on the job, is once again awakened by a pesty civilian in need of help, this time an old man with a runaway seeing-eye-dog that has ADHD. What hi-jinx and misadventures will SuperMilo get into this time around? Also includes a gallery of SuperMilo art and submitted fan art this issue! When a lazy and self-absorbed house cat is suddenly given intelligence and super powers, Twin City and nearby Clemmons gain a new so-called superhero – and super nuisance! Will SuperMilo’s friends be able to help him learn that being a hero is more than looking good for the camera, or will he destroy his beloved city in the process?
